## Command to create react app:

npx create-react-app netflix

## Benifit:

create project app gives you project scafold.
It uses webpack as an bundlers.
also it provides, react testing library support scafold.

## Other:

use webpack as bundler, earlier we have used parcel.
vite is also an bundler can be used.

ES7+ React/Redux/React-Native extension needed to use rafce command

- react arrow function component export

TO host your site with firebase Hosting, you need the firebase CLI
npm install -g firebase-tools

// redux store setup
npm i -D @react/toolkit
npm i react-redux

// Forms
Use formic library for long forms in react

// Firebase Setup
npm install firebase
create new project to websupport
copy configuration from firebase to project
firebase login
firebase init
enable authentication in firebase

